  "description": "Use this skill when bulk-migrating financial account data into Salesforce FSC \u2014 including FinancialAccount, FinancialHolding, FinancialAccountRole, FinancialAccountTransaction, and balance history records. Trigger keywords: ETL load FSC, migrate holdings, bulk insert financial accounts, data migration rollup lock, FinancialAccountBalance import. NOT for financial account configuration or FSC data model reference.",
